                "labels": [
                    {
                        "purpose": "M+ Sigg Collection",
                        "text": "In this early performance, Lin Yilin moves a temporary wall brick by brick across a busy road in Guangzhou. In doing so, he forces pedestrians and drivers to move around him, highlighting an individual’s labour against the backdrop of urban development. This work is a key example of the artist’s practice of integrating performance art and video."
                    },
